data.description: Create new family memories in this classic Chicago bungalow in the highly sought after Portage Park. Portage park is known for its family neighborhoods adjacent to the beautiful Portage Park that is surrounded by restaurants and shops. The area is home to thorp elementary school. This jumbo bungalow has its original charm with modern updates and boasts 5 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The updated kitchen has cherry wood cabinets with granite tops and stainless steel appliances. With a large living room and dining room you will have enough room to entertain family and guests. The partially finished basement is an open canvas ready for new ideas to make the space your own. The outdoor space and patio is perfect for summer fun. Come and see what makes this classic Chicago bungalow a great home. Motivated** Seller due to relocation.
